text: Shahidullah Khan is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Sirajganj-5. ==Career== Khan was elected to parliament from Sirajganj-5 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Shahidullah Khan
